accessibility.text: The real time breakthrough tool, for visualising and interact with your project environment.

Not only allows you to navigate almost infinitely, but also you can change, scenes in real time (day-night), change materials to the surfaces, input metadata to your projects, and more importantly you can navigate freely all the way through the virtual world with a 4K definition vision quality.
